verbose_text: Interestingly, TAPI-0 did not inhibit constitutive shedding of CD200 by Hek293 cells in serum-free conditions, suggesting the mechanism (s) of constitutive shedding is (are) distinct from PMA induced CD200 shedding in Hek293 cells.
